OctreeNode size = 26 bytes
26 * 8^4 (octree with four levels) * 16^3 (amount of chunks) = 1.51e9 = about 1.5 GB

Raw Voxel Data
Voxel size = 1 byte
1 * 16^3 (chunk size) * 16^3 (amount of chunks) = 16,777,216 = about 0.02 GB

